## 6. Error Handling Contract

| Failure mode | Behavior |
|-------------|----------|
| Channel throws synchronously | Caught by `Promise.allSettled`, logged, other channels proceed |
| Channel hangs (no timeout) | Lamorak's concurrency model enforces per-channel timeout |
| Webhook returns 4xx | Logged, no retry (client error) |
| Webhook returns 5xx | Retried with backoff (channel-internal) |
| File write fails (disk full) | Logged, pipeline continues |
| All channels fail | Pipeline still completes normally — notifications are best-effort |
| No channels configured | Router is null, no notification code executes |

---

## 7. YAML Config (Integration with Bors)

